Happy International Yoga Day! ✨🧘🏻‍♀️
Yoga isn’t just a routine; it’s the ultimate way to connect with yourself, inside and out. Whether it’s a calming stretch or a power pose, find what makes you feel strong and balanced.
Take a moment today to honor your body, mind, and soul — and let yoga be your guide.

latestPosts.caption:
Not every place makes you feel instantly at home, but this one did.
Trisara by @lohono_stays (tucked away in Devghar near Aamby Valley) was exactly what I needed for the perfect monsoon weekend. 🌧✨

I’m super picky about the places I stay at. I need space, comfort, and little thoughtful details that make it special.
And this one just got it all right. The perfect slow mornings with a view, it felt like a dream.

To the first man who taught me strength with softness - Dad, you’re my forever standard.
And to the man who’s raising our little ones with the same kind of quiet magic… thank you for making fatherhood look so effortlessly graceful.

Two amazing fathers, two kinds of love, both priceless.
Happy Father’s Day 🤍

latestPosts.caption:
Gin’s always been my drink—light, crisp, and just the right kind of refreshing.
And once I found Zoya, there was no looking back. 🍸
It’s smooth, with that perfect hint of boldness that keeps things interesting—whether I’m catching up with friends or enjoying a relaxing date night, Zoya always fits the vibe.

This World Gin Day, I’m toasting to good times, great company, and the gin that gets it just right.
Live, love, rejoice—with @zoyagin.life in hand.🍹

Last few dates have been unforgettable! NMACC Art cafe in Mumbai is where art meets the vibe and the food, of course. 🎨✨
From the art-inspired plating to their flavourful, thoughtfully crafted dishes, every bite here is a masterpiece. The ambiance is modern, welcoming, and effortlessly stylish, a perfect blend of culture, comfort, and culinary delight.
If you’re in Mumbai and craving food that speaks to your senses as much as the surroundings, this is the place to be. @nmacc.india

latestPosts.caption:
Still soaking it all in — what a special trip to London!
A huge thanks to the @icc for inviting me to witness history in the making at the Hall of Fame ceremony.
To be in the same room as cricketing legends were celebrated was truly surreal.
Cricket is the soul of India, and watching icons from around the world being honoured for their craft was nothing short of magical.
#WTC25 #ICCHallOfFame
